WEBVTT

00:03.340 --> 00:05.269
Hey, Ma.

00:09.902 --> 00:12.964
Ma, where's that little
green bag I left in here?

00:12.989 --> 00:15.549
It had my, uh... school supplies in it.

00:15.550 --> 00:18.610
I flushed your school
supplies down the toilet.

00:18.849 --> 00:21.419
- What?
- And the $12,000 that was in there,

00:21.420 --> 00:23.150
I donated to the church.

00:23.175 --> 00:25.443
No, no, no, no, Ma,
you don't understand.

00:25.468 --> 00:27.316
I have to answer for that, Ma.

00:27.341 --> 00:29.870
You told me that you
were selling sneakers!

00:32.362 --> 00:34.647
Listen, I knew you'd be
trippin' if I told you the truth.

00:34.672 --> 00:37.448
Look, Ma, there ain't no jobs out there

00:37.473 --> 00:39.672
payin' no real money, Ma.
I'm doin' what I gotta do.

00:39.682 --> 00:41.881
Even after what happened to your father?

00:41.882 --> 00:43.082
Look, I don't use, I sell.

00:45.721 --> 00:47.051
Get out of my house.

00:47.939 --> 00:49.209
There's your stuff.

00:51.744 --> 00:54.244
Get out of my house!

00:58.832 --> 01:01.114
There's nothing
stronger than a mother's love

01:01.139 --> 01:03.305
except a mother's disappointment.

01:04.202 --> 01:06.392
And that's the cold, hard truth,

01:06.417 --> 01:07.939
even for an OG.

01:08.224 --> 01:10.724
♪ The Last O.G. 2x08 ♪
<font color="#808080">Mama Said Knock You Out</font>

01:10.749 --> 01:13.249
- Synced and corrected by<font color="#00BFFF"> Firefly</font> -
